<b><i>Jazz and Wordsmith Journey</i></b>: DJ Jeannie Hopper has entered something of a blue note wormhole, bringing you selections by jazz musicians and wordsmiths from across as many decades as the genres allow. Newer tunes from Francisco Mela and Laurie Anderson stand alongside classics by Umar Bin Hassan and Baba Israel, along with more cross-generational tunes to upset your every notion of linear time.
